the x3 also fulfills the brand's reputation for modern luxury with a long list of conveniences, exquisite comfort, premium interior materials and near-flawless build quality.the front seats are comfortable and firm, with sufficient support for sporty driving.the added features and prestige of the bmw brand also make the x3 more expensive than similarly sporty entry-level luxury suvs like the infiniti ex35 and acura rdx.in crash testing conducted by the insurance institute for highway safety, the x3 was awarded the highest rating of "good" for protection in both frontal offset and side impacts.among small luxury crossover suvs, the x3 has no equal when it comes to arcing along a curvy road, thanks to the superior steering feel, ideal suspension tuning and eager engine power output.its sporty handling and steering, powerful engine, added utility and fun-to-drive nature are all bmw hallmarks.stand-alone options are also available and include 19-inch alloy wheels with higher-performance tires, a premium audio system, hd radio, a navigation system, a heated steering wheel, adaptive xenon headlights and front and rear parking sensors.included as standard features are 17-inch alloy wheels, a panoramic sunroof, automatic headlights, heated side mirrors, automatic climate control, leatherette (premium vinyl) upholstery, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, eight-way-adjustable power front seats with driver memory settings, full power accessories, keyless entry and a 10-speaker cd/mp3 player with an auxiliary audio jack.interior design and special features: the 2009 x3's interior is attractive and fitted with top-notch materials.rear-seat side airbags are available as an option.power is routed through either a six-speed manual or a six-speed automatic transmission with manual shift control.safety: standard safety equipment for the x3 includes antilock disc brakes, automatic brake drying, front-seat side airbags, full-length side curtain airbags, active front-seat head restraints, stability control and hill descent control.the premium package includes leather upholstery, auto-dimming mirrors, ambient lighting and bluetooth.one by-product of the superb handling is a less-than-luxurious ride quality.the x3's straight-6 delivers spirited power over the majority of its rpm range, while the automatic transmission's gearchanges are caffeinated in their eagerness.